```

### Example 1: Remove

```js
let arr = [1,2,3,4];
arr.splice(1,2);

console.log(arr); // [1,4]
```

### Example 2: Add

```js
let arr = [1,4];
arr.splice(1,0,2,3);

console.log(arr); // [1,2,3,4]
```

### Example 3: Replace

```js
arr.splice(1,2,"A","B");
```

вњ” Returns: removed elements
вњ” Changes original вљ пёЏ

---

## рџ”№ 6. `sort()`

```js
